{"tid":492720,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"曖昧時比拍拖時更開心","createTime":"2017-12-07T21:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T08:28:21.000Z","uid":34399,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5fef248a06d5f3e04d0b57e361fe5e7a0aec8d58","tid":492720,"uid":34399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T21:33:12.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過<br />\n曖昧果陣比起一齊左更sweet更有傾有講<br />\n一段時間段關係都係咁<br />\n然後就分左手"},{"pid":"9b15da616b67516e0bbb68c3b9a9e0f218e3defb","tid":492720,"uid":48039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人試過<br />\n曖昧果陣比起一齊左更sweet更有傾有講<br />\n一段時間段關係都係咁<br />\n然後就分左手</blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<br />\n我都直接同佢講話覺得拍左拖之後<br />\n反而好似衰左 <br />\n唔緊要啦 都就散"},{"pid":"c4211de405d7b8e8bf19734e6870331a5ca99b67","tid":492720,"uid":34399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:54:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人試過<br />\n曖昧果陣比起一齊左更sweet更有傾有講<br />\n一段時間段關係都係咁<br />\n然後就分左手</blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<br />\n我都直接同佢講話覺得拍左拖之後<br />\n反而好似衰左 <br />\n唔緊要啦 都就散</blockquote><br />\n拍之前都仲會搵機會約出來<br />\n但一齊左後佢反而求求奇無所謂咁"},{"pid":"7909e193d202e3acb676aed178800aa97192ee31","tid":492720,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:17:55.000Z","msg":"愛像霧裡看花朦朧才美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fed2e07a17c32dc89a3b600c6673d37986f355","tid":492720,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"不過<br />\n不夠盲目 就不能淪陷<br />\n理智在愛情裡面 從來就不是關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1537ed5fa8820a82227e43faa455e977787342e","tid":492720,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}